es: 1</p>\n						<p>Hello,</p>\n<p>I have several problems with the site map generated for this site, as well as with the plugin itself.</p>\n<p>First of all, please note that there is a site map for each language:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap.xml\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap.xml</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.textile-du-maine.com/en/sitemap.xml\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://www.textile-du-maine.com/en/sitemap.xml</a></p>\n<p>1. Duplicate page listings</p>\n<p>All pages are listed twice in each site map. Google shows the French site having 39 pages and the English site having 38 pages, though each site has about half the number of pages.</p>\n<p>2. Strange structure of site map (and illogical placement of double pages)</p>\n<p>I don&#8217;t understand the logic behind the site map sub-pages. It doesn&#8217;t correspond to the structure of the site. Also, underneath different sub-pages of the site map, you find duplicates of the pages, but this is not consistently done. For example, the page &#8220;<a href=\"https://www.textile-du-maine.com/mentions_legales/&#038;#8221\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://www.textile-du-maine.com/mentions_legales/&#038;#8221</a>; is doubled WITHIN the &#8220;01&#8221; sub-page. On the other hand, the doubles for the &#8220;contact&#8221; page are found in two different sub-pages (&#8220;11&#8221; and &#8220;03&#8221;). Here is the structure of the sub-pages of the site map:</p>\n<p>URL of sub-sitemap	Last modified (GMT)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-misc.xml\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-misc.xml</a>	2020-02-16 15:08<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-pt-page-2020-01.xml\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-pt-page-2020-01.xml</a>	2020-02-08 14:09<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-pt-page-2019-11.xml\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-pt-page-2019-11.xml</a>	2020-02-16 15:08<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-pt-page-2019-09.xml\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-pt-page-2019-09.xml</a>	2020-02-16 09:24<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-pt-page-2018-03.xml\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://www.textile-du-maine.com/sitemap-pt-page-2018-03.xml</a>	2020-02-06 23:29</p>\n<p>3. Problems with Links on Plugin Settings page</p>\n<p>On the plugin settings page, all the links are broken underneath the titles, &#8220;About this plugin&#8221; and &#8220;Sitemap Resources.&#8221;</p>\n<p>Details of installation:<br />\n&#8211; WordPress 5.3.2 running Bridge theme.<br />\n&#8211; Plugin Version 4.1.0</p>\n<p>Best regards,</p>\n<p>Robert</p>\n						\n					\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"rreedmeister\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:28;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n\n					\n					\n\n					\n					\n					\n				\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:104:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/showing-erro-not-loading-sitemap-with-setting-a-cookies-free-domain/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"Showing erro Not Loading Sitemap With setting a cookies free domain\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:104:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/showing-erro-not-loading-sit